From 1a8396110f556aa23d92d3ba54fb3b5cf4ac4d4e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Barry Friedman (friedman)" <friedman@cisco.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Mar 2026 15:27:01 -0700
Subject: zebra: Add vid and BR_PORT_DELETE support for EVPN MH FPM

Add per-VLAN bridge port attribute support for EVPN Multihoming:

- Add vid field to dplane_br_port_info and dplane_ctx_get_br_port_vlan_id()
  accessor
- Add DPLANE_OP_BR_PORT_DELETE enum and dplane_br_port_delete() API
- Update dplane_br_port_update() to accept vid parameter
- Add zebra_evpn_es_br_port_dplane_update_all_vids() to send per-VID
  updates for SHL/DF on VLAN member add/remove
- Update zebra_evpn_es_br_port_dplane_clear() to send per-VID deletes
- Update zebra_evpn_vl_mbr_ref() to send per-VID br_port update on
  VLAN member addition
- Update zebra_evpn_vl_mbr_deref() to send per-VID br_port delete on
  VLAN member removal

Ported from cisco_202405_dev commit:
  991145f0f2 - Add DPLANE_OP_BR_PORT_DELETE for explicit VID delete

Signed-off-by: Ben Friedman <friedman@cisco.com>
(cherry picked from commit 087167eb89bed5925fa064ff8bc489eca8112697)
Signed-off-by: Tamer Ahmed <tamerahmed@microsoft.com>

